snippet.title: The Mask Reveals Disgusting Face (v 1.0) (my indie game)
snippet.description: The Mask Reveals Disgusting Face is a horror adventure, with pixel graphics and quest-like gameplay (with some action parts). The game is about a depressed person named Gary, who decided to spend some time in empty house outside the town. Bad idea. http://gamejolt.com/games/adventure/the-mask-reveals-disgusting-face/22523/
